
<div class="center-div">
  <h2>Merry Christmas <%= @member.goes_by %>!</h2>
  <form class="form-horizontal" id="member-form" action="/members/<%= @member.permalink %>" method="POST" name="member_form">
    <fieldset>
      <p>We're bringing some order to chaos of the cousin gift exchange this year.</p>
      <p>Per usual, you have to be at Grandma's on Christmas Day to participate.</p>
      <p>Well, if you won't be at Grandma's but can't bare to be left out, I suppose you can play too but just make sure your wrapped gift gets to Grandma's on the 25th.<p>
      <p>The budget is $30.00. Drawing results will be announced in two days or so, you'll get another email.</p>
      <p>So, are you <i>in</i> on the Cousin Gift Exchange?</p>
      <div class="controls">
        <div class="member-form">
          <input type="radio" class="member-yes-radio" id="radio-0" name="reply[<%= @member.id %>]" required="true" value="true"><label for="radio-0">Yes</label><br>
          <input type="radio" class="member-no-radio" id="radio-0" name="reply[<%= @member.id %>]" required="true" value="false"><label for="radio-0">No</label><br>

          <div class="member-no-response">
            <p>Bummer, maybe next year!</p>
          </div>

          <div class="member-yes-response">
            <p>Sweet! Provide some of your recent interests here so the person who "draws" you has some ideas:</p>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="member-interests" name="interests[<%= @member.id %>]" rows="4" cols="50" placeholder="e.g. ironic tee-shirts, justin bieber, gourmet BBQ sauce, etc (keep the $30 budget in mind)"></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>
        <%= render partial: "dependents_form" %>

        <input class="btn btn-success btn-large" id="form-button" type="submit" value="Submit">
      </div>
    </fieldset>
  </form>
</div>
